             was indicted for <rs id="t18000115-4-off17" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000115-4-off17" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000115-4-off17" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000115-4-victim72" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Robson
                        <interp inst="t18000115-4-victim72" type="surname" value="Robson"></interp>
